N'Golo Kante: Leicester City set to sign Caen midfielder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Leicester City are set to sign Caen midfielder N'Golo Kante for an undisclosed fee after he passed a medical at the Premier League club.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
BBC Radio Leicester reports the 24-year-old will join the Foxes for a fee of about Â£6m.
